headline: PNC Bank Survey Offers Insights, Analysis on Financial Wellness Mindset Among U.S. Workers and Employers
summary: PNC Bank today released findings from its third annual Financial Wellness in the Workplace Report entitled, "What today's workers value most, across generations," which summarizes survey data and in-depth interviews from more than 1,000 U.S. workers and more than 500 U.S. employers to better understand the financial health and wellness of today's workforce.

headline: Diversified Banks Stocks Q2 Results: Benchmarking PNC Financial Services Group (NYSE:PNC)
summary: Wrapping up Q2 earnings, we look at the numbers and key takeaways for the diversified banks stocks, including PNC Financial Services Group (NYSE:PNC) and its peers.
